summary: An ordinance relating to the percentage of lot occupancy of a portion of Tract 22, Spring Hill Villa Tracts, located on the west side of 51st venue Southwest, between West Dawson Street and West Hudson Street; rezoning said property from Area District "A" to Area District "B" and amending Ordinance No. 45382 as amended, by adding thereto one new section numbered 17 (6-Z).
